UID:event_313820429@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260320T024540Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260323T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260323T210000
SUMMARY:Bowling @ Windsor Bowling Center 🎳 🍻
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\nWindsor Bowling Center\, Sonoma County
 's only family-owned bowling center and your ultimate destination in the h
 eart of wine country! Just seconds off the freeway and next to the Holiday
  Inn Express\, we offer fun for everyone with Black Light Mini\, Escape Ro
 oms\, pool tables\, arcade games and FULL BAR!!\n\nCome down for some bowl
 ing action! All skill levels welcome and bumpers are available 😁\n\nI w
 ill be bowling 3 games and post the lane assignment in the comments.\n\nWh
 en you arrive tell the front desk the lane you are on and how many games y
 ou would like to bowl and they will get you set up with some bowling shoes
 . Be sure to wear or bring socks!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/sonoma-marin-brat-pack/events/3138204
 29/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260317T175513Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260317T175513Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/sonoma-marin-brat-pack/
UID:event_313644320@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260320T024540Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260324T181500
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260324T203000
SUMMARY:Trivia at Trailhead (Novato)
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\n🎉 Join Us for Trivia Night! 🧠☕
 ️\nThis event is cross-posted with Sonoma Marin Brat Pack\, Marin County
  Millennials\, and North Bay 20s30s Meetup\, so RSVPs may not reflect the 
 full crowd.\n\nWe’re Team Quizzards! I’ll be at most events\, and if I
  can’t make it\, you’ll still find some friendly regulars there. Look 
 for us at the back of the coffee shop — come say hi and join the fun! 
 🎉\n\n🕡 Trivia kicks off promptly at 6:30 PM\, so swing by a bit earl
 ier if you'd like to grab a drink or something tasty to eat before we get 
 started. I plan to be there at 6 pm to try to get us a good table .\n📍 
 Location:\nTrailhead Coffee\n127 San Marin Drive\, Novato\, CA\nBring your
  friends\, your appetite\, and your A-game — see you there! 🙌
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/sonoma-marin-brat-pack/events/3136443
 20/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260305T032738Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260305T032738Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
