SUMMARY:Karaoke @ Ricardos 🎤🍺
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\nCome out for some karaoke. This is an 
 early all ages karaoke event. It nice to find some karaoke that doesn't st
 art after 9pm!\n\nWhether you want to sing or just hang out for some fun i
 t's a good time.
